  "body": "## ملخص / Summary\n\nيكمّل هذا الـ PR تكامل **V3 Revenue Machine** فوق V1+V2 — دورة كاملة من Lead إلى Retainer.\n\n### ما الذي أُضيف (82 ملف، 2068 سطر)\n\n| المجال | الملفات الجديدة |\n|--------|----------------|\n| **CRM Ledger** | `data/crm/` — leads, accounts, interactions, opportunities + pipeline schema |\n| **Analytics** | `data/analytics/daily_metrics.jsonl` |\n| **Prospects** | `data/prospects/` — ICP seed accounts (Saudi) + lead scoring output |\n| **Case Studies** | `data/case_studies/`, `docs/case-studies/` templates AR+EN + generated |\n| **Frontend Pages** | `/book`, `/diagnostic`, `/case-studies/[slug]` + `/case-studies` listing |\n| **API Route** | `frontend/src/app/api/leads/route.ts` — Lead Capture endpoint |\n| **UI Components** | `LeadCaptureForm.tsx`, `DiagnosticIntakeForm.tsx` |\n| **Frontend Lib** | `leadValidation.ts`, `utm.ts` |\n| **Scripts (15)** | CRM append/report/next-actions, offer builder, KPI log/dashboard, case study builder (Arabic slug fixed), lead scoring, readiness checks, daily command center, prospect drafts |\n| **Delivery OS** | `delivery/` — playbooks per package (diagnostic, pilot, executive-os, custom-ai) + client acceptance criteria + weekly update template |\n| **Security** | `security/` — secret handling policy, AI guardrails, launch security checklist |\n| **Offer Templates** | `templates/offers/` — 5 templates (diagnostic, pilot, executive-os, custom-ai, enterprise) |\n| **Docs Launch** | `docs/launch/` — 9 documents (100-day map, war room, revenue machine V3 AR, CRM pipeline, daily prospecting OS…) |\n| **Ops** | KPI scorecard, weekly growth review, onboarding checklist, executive report template |\n| **Sales** | Call script, WhatsApp sequence, email sequence, proposal, SOW, objection handling |\n| **Marketing** | Brand messaging system, LinkedIn 30-day calendar, SEO+UTM plan |\n| **GitHub Actions** | `dealix-daily-growth-os`, `dealix-launch-readiness`, `dealix-security-smoke` |\n| **.gitignore** | Exceptions for `data/crm`, `analytics`, `case_studies`, `prospects`, `frontend/src/lib/` |\n\n### اختبارات تشغيلية / Smoke Tests Passed\n\n```\n✅ python scripts/dealix_v3_readiness_check.py   → OK: Dealix V3 revenue machine files are present\n✅ python scripts/dealix_crm_append_lead.py       → Lead created, score=100\n✅ python scripts/dealix_crm_pipeline_report.py   → Total leads: 1, Qualified: 1\n✅ python scripts/dealix_crm_next_actions.py      → Next action displayed\n✅ python scripts/dealix_offer_builder.py         → Offer written to out/offers/\n✅ python scripts/dealix_kpi_log.py               → KPI entry logged\n✅ python scripts/dealix_kpi_dashboard.py         → Dashboard rendered\n✅ python scripts/dealix_case_study_builder.py    → Case study written (Arabic slug fixed)\n✅ python scripts/dealix_lead_scoring.py          → 3 prospects scored and written to CSV\n```\n\n### الدورة التشغيلية / Revenue Loop\n\n```\nLead → Qualification → Conversation → Diagnostic → Proposal → Delivery → Retainer\n```\n\nhttps://claude.ai/code/session_01LQ2CmHDDuACmW75Eev7Hx1\n\n---\n_Generated by [Claude Code](https://claude.ai/code/session_01LQ2CmHDDuACmW75Eev7Hx1)_",
